> Delivery OS v4 router: the single entrypoint, **capped ~100 lines**. It **ANSWERS or POINTS, never restates.**
> Canonical truth = `docs/` (project) + `../ecosystem-architecture/` (portfolio). If this file
> disagrees with a canonical source, the **canonical source wins — fix this file.**
> **Two halves (v4):** §1–4, 7-intent, 8 are the **HAND half** (identity, mission, north star, invariants,
> pointers — founder-signed, slow). §5, §6 roster, §9, and §7's edge facts are the **DERIVED half** — rendered
> from disk by `.claude/tools/render-kernel.mjs`; **hand-editing a derived section is a fail-closed drift-lint
> error**, and `os_version` derives from the `.claude/.verify-config.json` pin, never from prose.
> *(v4 deleted the old "hand-maintained — no generator reconciles it" header: that sentence was the root cause
> of the costliest cross-repo incident on record, self-documented and propagated verbatim into two consumers.)*
